<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Achievements | Engineering Science</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --accent: #2563eb;
            --dark: #1e293b;
            --grey: #64748b;
            --light: #f8fafc;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--dark);
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        header {
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--light);
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 2.5rem; }
        h2 { 
            font-size: 1.4rem; 
            color: var(--accent); 
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
            padding-left: 15px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .category-intro { color: var(--grey); font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 20px; }

        /* Academic Styling */
        .year-block { margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .year-title { font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .highlight-rank { color: #0f172a; font-weight: 600; display: block; }
        .prizes { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #475569; margin-top: 5px; }

        /* List Styling */
        ul { padding-left: 20px; margin: 10px 0; }
        li { margin-bottom: 8px; }

        /* Competition Table */
        .comp-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .comp-table td { padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; }
        .comp-year { width: 80px; color: var(--grey); font-weight: 500; }
        .comp-rank { font-weight: bold; color: #111; width: 180px; }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .comp-table tr { display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 10px 0; }
            .comp-rank { width: 100%; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Achievements</h1>
        <p>Engineering Science & Applied Mathematics</p>
    </header>

    <section>
        <h2>🎓 Academic Excellence</h2>
        <p class="category-intro">Recognition for top academic performance and module-specific mastery.</p>
        
        <div class="year-block">
            <span class="year-title">2025</span>
            <span class="highlight-rank">Most Outstanding Performance for Level 2.2 in Engineering Science</span>
            <div class="prizes">
                Director’s List • Module Prize for Applied Mathematics 3 • Module Prize for Microcontroller and Interfacing • Module Prize for Physics 2
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="year-block">
            <span class="year-title">2024</span>
            <span class="highlight-rank">Most Outstanding Performance for Level 1.2 in Engineering Science</span>
            <span class="highlight-rank">3rd Most Outstanding Performance for Level 2.1</span>
            <div class="prizes">
                Director’s List (Multiple) • Module Prize for Physics 1 • Module Prize for Applied Mathematics 2A • Module Prize for Analogue Electronics
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="year-block">
            <span class="year-title">2023</span>
            <span class="highlight-rank">Most Outstanding Performance for Level 1.1 in Engineering Science</span>
            <div class="prizes">
                Director’s List • Module Prize for Applied Mathematics 1 • Module Prize for Electrical Engineering Fundamentals • Module Prize for Engineering and Society • Module Prize for Mechanical Engineering Fundamentals
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>🏆 Competitions</h2>
        <p class="category-intro">Awards and rankings from national and international engineering challenges.</p>
        <table class="comp-table">
            <tr>
                <td class="comp-year">2025</td>
                <td class="comp-rank">2nd Runner Up</td>
                <td>BusTech Grand Challenge (Tertiary Category)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="comp-year">2023</td>
                <td class="comp-rank">First Place</td>
                <td>National Robotics Competition (Tertiary Division)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="comp-year">2023</td>
                <td class="comp-rank">First Place</td>
                <td>Global Robotic Games (Mobile Robotics IV)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="comp-year">2022</td>
                <td class="comp-rank">Gold Award</td>
                <td>Young Inventor’s Journal</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="comp-year">2020</td>
                <td class="comp-rank">1st Runner Up</td>
                <td>Engineering Innovation Challenge</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="comp-year">2020</td>
                <td class="comp-rank">Silver Award</td>
                <td>Indonesia International Applied Science Project Olympiad</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>🏅 Other Honors</h2>
        <p class="category-intro">Additional awards in design, mathematics, and science.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>SUTD-SST-NP Big D Camp:</strong> Design Excellence Award (2019-2022)</li>
            <li><strong>Singapore and Asian Schools Math Olympiad:</strong> Gold, Silver, and Bronze Awards</li>
            <li><strong>Australian Mathematics Competition:</strong> Distinction (2020)</li>
            <li><strong>SST Book Prizes:</strong> Mathematics & Electronics (2021)</li>
            <li><strong>Young Inventors Journal:</strong> Gold Award (2022)</li>
            <li><strong>Engineering Innovation Challenge:</strong> 1st Runner Up (2021)</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
